#### Route B: Agent Teams (`--team`)

IMPORTANT: This route uses Claude Code Agent Teams (experimental). Requires `CLAUDE_CODE_EXPERIMENTAL_AGENT_TEAMS=1`.

If `CLAUDE_CODE_EXPERIMENTAL_AGENT_TEAMS=1` is not set, abort with:
